a-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA%2Fvideos&d=MDE%2Bq9SdTpebmtK%2F5E3Z78n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=fa8c22f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA/videos</a><br />\n<br />\n香港戒色論壇<br />\n<a href=\"http://noj1314.258club.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnoj1314.258club.com&d=MDE%2Bq9SdTpebmtK%2F5E3Z78n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=af9788d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://noj1314.258club.com</a><br />\n<br />\n秦東魁老師<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLyVAEphpUDM&d=MDE%2Bq9SdTpebmtK%2F5E3Z78n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=05eb0a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM</a><br />\n<br />\n戒色吧<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%BD%E4%C9%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Ff%3Fkw%3D%25BD%25E4%25C9%25AB&d=MDE%2Bq9SdTpebmtK%2F5E3Z78n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0082f7c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%BD%E4%C9%AB</a>"},{"pid":"2b88aa7338226d6791c9d4d0ad1591a0e62ceed6","tid":951194,"uid":35484,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:47:37.000Z","msg":"戒Ｊ需知： <br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞，但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢遺唔當破戒，意淫都傷身，睇ＡＶ唔Ｊ一樣咁傷身 ，中醫：心動則精自走<br />\n<br />\n做愛都傷身，所以我地戒Ｊ恢復身體，身體好虧既戒返２年，之後再節制性行為，咁就唔會出症狀，飛翔老師推薦一月2次，就是腎氣充足的情況下，這樣對身體傷害較小。<br />\n<br />\n戒色唔係做和尚，係先禁慾養返好個身體，再同老婆／女友節制性生活，咁就唔會出症狀<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，如果你忍唔到，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁期間扑野唔算破戒，但你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將（戒為良藥）睇一次<br />\n學習提升覺悟，覺悟降伏心魔，唔睇（戒為良藥），基本上只係等破戒"},{"pid":"ca313c858b3981ec5888328812e34378a0659240","tid":951194,"uid":121473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:54:10.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"001cea3840b4552174ff0642d30bd46c969440c5","tid":951194,"uid":133950,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"推 我估我吾戒丁 應該已經入左土。 但問題根據自己逛戒色吧的多年經驗，夢遺或者遺精係每位戒丁者都會遇到既問題。我自己亦好難完全杜絕呢個症狀。不過貌似呢個問題會隨著時間推移 慢慢消失"},{"pid":"20af7a220ee4f286efd4a935851b9bf5b0937bd1","tid":951194,"uid":35484,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"001cea3840b4552174ff0642d30bd46c969440c5","tid":951194,"uid":133950,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"推 我估我吾戒丁 應該已經入左土。 但問題根據自己逛戒色吧的多年經驗，夢遺或者遺精係每位戒丁者都會遇到既問題。我自己亦好難完全杜絕呢個症狀。不過貌似呢個問題會隨著時間推移 慢慢消失"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n夢遺係自然生理反應，唔算破戒"},{"pid":"93dd5115bf3d05768c292865f87fbbacd28acc16","tid":951194,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b50f510a984902651b2e1d39c3f2f516e6e5c68","tid":951194,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"睇完個post都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265f8f351aa591fc34effd190af28b602c365260","tid":951194,"uid":133950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20af7a220ee4f286efd4a935851b9bf5b0937bd1","tid":951194,"uid":35484,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"001cea3840b4552174ff0642d30bd46c969440c5","tid":951194,"uid":133950,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"推 我估我吾戒丁 應該已經入左土。 但問題根據自己逛戒色吧的多年經驗，夢遺或者遺精係每位戒丁者都會遇到既問題。我自己亦好難完全杜絕呢個症狀。不過貌似呢個問題會隨著時間推移 慢慢消失"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n夢遺係自然生理反應，唔算破戒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:39:55.000Z","msg":"但問題夢遺會生理地和心理地打擊一個戒丁康復緊的人， 夢遺完個人會累d，雖然對比打丁傷害細左太多太多。但會有少少。"},{"pid